Kafka topic per department, unified schema in Apache Avro:
{
  "namespace": "enterprise.data",
  "type": "record",
  "name": "UnifiedEvent",
  "fields": [
    {"name": "timestamp", "type": "long"},
    {"name": "source", "type": "string"},
    {"name": "payload", "type": "string"}
  ]
}
